      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "A Song of Red and Fire",
        "Client": "Solitary Composer",
        "Description": "Can you hear that? The perfect\r\nmelody of flowing lava, smoldering\r\nash, and the bassy rumblings of\r\nthe volcano all accompanied by\r\nthe sound of Volvidon rolling\r\naround. Bravo! BRAVO!",
        "Target": "Hunt a Volvidon",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Chanson de sang et de feu",
        "Client": "Compositeur solitaire",
        "Description": "Aaah... La douce m\u00E9lodie de la\r\nlave en fusion r\u00E9duisant tout\r\nen cendres au rythme des\r\ngrondements du volcan et du\r\nbruit du Volvidon roulant\r\n\u00E7a et l\u00E0... C\u0027est absolument\r\ndivin ! Chapeau, l\u0027artiste !",
        "Target": "Chasser un Volvidon",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Cronache di lava e fuoco",
        "Client": "Compositore solitario",
        "Description": "La senti questa melodia? La\r\nlava che scorre, la cenere che\r\nbrucia e il borbottio del\r\nvulcano... Accompagnati dal\r\nritmo dei passi di un\r\nVolvidon. Bravi! BIS!",
        "Target": "Caccia un Volvidon",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Das Lied von Rot und Feuer",
        "Client": "Einsamer Komponist",
        "Description": "H\u00F6rst du das? Die perfekte\r\nMelodie flie\u00DFender Lava,\r\ngl\u00FChende Asche und das Grum-\r\nmeln eines Vulkans, begleitet\r\nvom Klang eines umherrollenden\r\nVolvidons. Bravo! BRAVO!",
